freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I got caught up on other vaccinations a month after my 2nd dose of the Pfizer vaccine. On 2/25/21 I received my overdue 2nd dose of Shingrix and a flu vaccination. As a result I feel awful. I felt fine with no symptoms before this.

The last 2 days I had some moderate  tightness in my lungs. I have a history of asthma and severe pneumonia though so it couldve been related/unrelated. Its better now. Ive been completely isolated at home since 3/2020 w/ zero people contact

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Had some unusual radiating nerve pain running into my left breast last night. I got the shot in left arm
My hearing is hypersensitive. Maybe due to headache.
